    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Trapped in a nightmarish world, you awaken to find yourself at the mercy of a sinister Game Master. &quot;Roll of Fate&quot; is a first-person, turn-based horror roguelike inspired by classic board games. Your only hope of freedom lies in playing the Game Master’s twisted game and surviving his malevolent challenge.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >&quot;How will you escape?&quot;</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each turn, the dice decide your fate. Roll to determine the number of actions you can take, whether it’s moving, utilizing cards or the unfortunate turn skip. Beware, for every move could bring you closer to freedom or doom, and the Game Master ensures no two games are ever the same.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3058820/extras/802890b9928cf4b3e6e7cfcbd1fc80c5.poster.avif?t=1751803754\" width=608 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3058820/extras/802890b9928cf4b3e6e7cfcbd1fc80c5.webm?t=1751803754\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3058820/extras/802890b9928cf4b3e6e7cfcbd1fc80c5.mp4?t=1751803754\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Throughout your journey, discover cards with the power to aid your escape. Use them wisely to gain advantages, such as additional extra actions, a compass, or a decoy to distract the Game Master from reaching you. But be cautious—each card carries an element of chance, and luck might not always be on your side.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3058820/extras/0de979b5aff3e7b452de4bbdba0de74c.webp?t=1751803754\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3058820/extras/0de979b5aff3e7b452de4bbdba0de74c.poster.avif?t=1751803754\" class=\"bb_img\" width=609 height=175 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With its chilling atmosphere, strategic gameplay, and changing map on every playthrough, &quot;Roll of Fate&quot; offers a unique blend of horror and strategy. Can you outwit the Game Master and reclaim your freedom, or will you be trapped in his eerie domain forever?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Turn-based gameplay with dice rolls determining actions</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dynamic challenges and an unpredictable Game Master</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Immersive horror atmosphere with high re-playability</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Achievement's to unlock dice customization options</p></li></ul>",
